Super Timeline Analysis in Timesketch
Learning Objectives
By completing this lab, you will:

Install and configure Timesketch for forensic timeline analysis
Import multiple forensic timeline data sources into Timesketch
Correlate events from different sources to identify attack patterns
Perform advanced super timeline analysis to reconstruct incident timelines
Prerequisites
Basic Linux command-line knowledge
Understanding of digital forensics concepts
Familiarity with log analysis and timeline reconstruction
Knowledge of common attack vectors and indicators of compromise
